DMS Dealer App Rules

1) AppShell rule:
AppShell MUST be rendered only in:
apps/dealer/app/(app)/layout.tsx

2) ModalShell rule:
ModalShell must NEVER be self-closing.
Always use:
<ModalShell ...>...</ModalShell>

3) Next.js cache rule:
Do NOT import `noStore` directly.
Always use:
import { unstable_noStore as noStore } from "next/cache"

4) Token styling rule:
No Tailwind palette colors.
Only CSS variables:
var(--surface)
var(--border)
var(--text)
var(--muted-text)
var(--ring)
